# content/glossary/

This directory holds one Markdown file per glossary term, written by the
glossary cron (`.github/workflows/glossary-cron.yml`).

Frontmatter schema is defined in `src/types/glossary.ts`. The cron writes
files; pages are statically generated at build time by reading them.

Empty until the bootstrap run; the `.gitkeep` keeps the dir tracked.
